OL,3,CVictims' commissioner Baroness Helen
OL,4,CNewlove dies
OL,6,FBaroness Helen Newlove, the victims'
OL,7,Fcommissioner for England and Wales,
OL,8,Fhas died following a short illness,
OL,9,Fher office has said.
OL,11,FThe peer, whose husband Garry was
OL,12,Fmurdered by a gang of teenagers in
OL,13,FWarrington in 2007, was appointed
OL,14,Fcommissioner in October 2023 and was
OL,15,Fdue to serve until the end of this
OL,16,Fyear.
OL,18,FHer office paid tribute to her as a
OL,19,F"committed and passionate advocate for
OL,20,Fvictims".
