OL,3,CVictims' commissioner Baroness Helen
OL,4,CNewlove dies
OL,6,FA statement read: "Under her
OL,7,Fleadership, the role of victims'
OL,8,Fcommissioner was transformed ` growing
OL,9,Fin stature, influence and authority.
OL,11,F"She reshaped the office into a
OL,12,Ftrusted voice and genuine force for
OL,13,Fvictims: one that stands firmly on
OL,14,Ftheir side, champions their rights,
OL,15,Fand holds the justice system to
OL,16,Faccount.
OL,18,FThis transformation stands as a
OL,19,Ftestament to her work and will remain
OL,20,Fher enduring legacy."
