OL,3,CVictims' commissioner Baroness Helen
OL,4,CNewlove dies
OL,6,FBaroness Newlove became a national
OL,7,Fvoice for victims, campaigning for
OL,8,Fauthorities to take action against
OL,9,Fpersistent anti-social behaviour and
OL,10,Fyouth violence following her husband's
OL,11,Fdeath in 2007.
OL,13,FThree teenagers were convicted of his
OL,14,Fmurder in January 2008, and Lady
OL,15,FNewlove was made a life peer for her
OL,16,Fwork on youth crime in 2010.
OL,18,FAmong the tributes, the deputy Prime
OL,19,FMinister Justice Secretary David Lammy
OL,20,Fsaid he is "deeply saddened".
OL,26,@|D@LOU|D@\O]
