OL,3,CVictims' commissioner Baroness Helen
OL,4,CNewlove dies
OL,6,FThe Deputy Prime Minister said: "As
OL,7,Fboth victims' commissioner, and Deputy
OL,8,FSpeaker in the House of Lords, Helen
OL,9,Fbrought unparalleled experience and
OL,10,Fdedication to her roles.
OL,12,F"She championed the rights of victims
OL,13,Fand witnesses and held agencies to
OL,14,Faccount.
OL,16,F"Her leadership shaped the Victims'
OL,17,FCode, strengthened victims' voices in
OL,18,Fthe criminal justice system, and
OL,19,Fensured that the Victims and Prisoners
OL,20,FAct progressed with victims' interests
OL,21,Fat its heart.
