OL,6,F"Helen was an extraordinary public
OL,7,Fservant whose life's work and her
OL,8,Flegacy are defined by courage,
OL,9,Fcompassion, and an unwavering
OL,10,Fcommitment to justice.
OL,12,F"My thoughts remain with her family
OL,13,Fand her loved ones at this incredibly
OL,14,Fdifficult time."
