OL,4,CNewlove dies
OL,6,FFormer prime minister David Cameron,
OL,7,Fwho appointed Barron Newlove as a peer
OL,8,Fin 2010, described her as a
OL,9,F"wonderful, warm, brave and plain
OL,10,Fspeaking" woman who turned the tragedy
OL,11,Fof losing her husband "into a second
OL,12,Flife of service."
OL,14,FHe said: "Service to her community, to
OL,15,Fthe country and to Parliament - but,
OL,16,Fmost of all, service to victims of
OL,17,Fcrime to make sure they got a proper
OL,18,Fhearing and a better deal.
