OL,3,CVictims' commissioner Baroness Helen
OL,4,CNewlove dies
OL,6,F"It was a privilege to meet her and an
OL,7,Fhonour to help her into a position
OL,8,Fwhere she could dedicate herself to
OL,9,Fthe service of others.
OL,11,F"My thoughts and heartfelt condolences
OL,12,Fare with Helen's husband, Paul, and
OL,13,Fher daughters, Zoe, Danielle and Amy.
OL,15,F"Helen leaves a legacy that they - and
OL,16,Fwe all - can be proud of.
OL,18,FLady Newlove was "such a very lovely
OL,19,Fperson", independent crossbencher
OL,20,FBaroness O'Loan said in a moving
OL,21,Ftribute.
