OL,3,CVictims' commissioner Baroness Helen
OL,4,CNewlove dies
OL,6,FThe former police ombudsman for
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland said: "May I pay
OL,8,Ftribute to Baroness Newlove, who was
OL,9,Fso brave and effective in all that she
OL,10,Fdid in this House and in her work for
OL,11,Fvictims after the murder of her
OL,12,Fbeloved husband, Garry.
OL,14,F"Helen had such compassion, such
OL,15,Fcourage, and she really was such a
OL,16,Fvery lovely person, that she will be
OL,17,Fsorely missed, not only by her family,
OL,18,Fto whom I'm sure we all send great
OL,19,Fsympathy, but also by so many of us in
OL,20,Fthis House and in the world beyond.
